The paper proposes a method for finding network structures that maximize the probabilistic soft margin, a discriminative score used in classification. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data mining (cs.DM), statistical learning (cs.SI), and information theory (cs.IT).
